claim.claim-text:
An operation method of a diagnosis imaging apparatus, the method comprising:
detecting a first point and a second point on a heart wall of a valve of interest in a 3D volume data of a heart of a subject;
rotating the 3D volume data to make a virtual line connecting the first point and the second point be parallel with a datum plane;
acquiring a 3D standard view of the valve of interest based on the rotated 3D volume data.
